            "title": "中國外長王毅：美國、伊朗都有重啟談判意願",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.PlKRhWwcV2.mqkcBiYrLA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/e2c30a0c8d7b888c9c507ba961488ebf\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E5%95%9F%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E6%84%8F%E9%A1%98-143222367.html",
